{"base_path":"/","components":null,"consumes":"[\"application/json;charset=UTF-8\",\"application/json\"]","definitions":{"ServerPhyInfo":{"properties":{"network_nodes":{"description":"**参数解释**:Tor信息。\n**取值范围**:多个ip信息,IPv4格式。","items":{"type":"string"},"type":"array"},"resource_id":{"description":"**参数解释**:Lite Server实例资源ID。\n**取值范围**:长度为[8,36]个字符。","type":"string"}},"type":"object"},"ServerPhyResponse":{"properties":{"servers":{"description":"**参数解释**:server列表。","items":{"$ref":"#/definitions/ServerPhyInfo"},"type":"array"}},"type":"object"}},"description":null,"group_id":"ade740e866904a7dbdaa5ec0f538d4d0","host":"modelarts.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com","id":"6868c2e344ff4f52b36fe3498747334a","info_version":"v1","method":"get","name":"GetTopologies","parameters":{"projectId":{"description":"**参数解释**:用户项目ID。获取方法请参见[获取项目ID和名称](modelarts_03_0147.xml)。\n**约束限制**:1 - 64字符,字母、数字和中划线。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","in":"path","name":"project_id","required":true,"type":"string"}},"paths":{"/v1/{project_id}/dev-servers/instance-physical-topologies":{"get":{"description":"查询实例的Tor信息接口用于获取指定实例的Top-of-Rack(Tor)交换机相关信息。该接口适用于以下场景:当用户需要了解实例连接的Tor交换机的详细信息,以便进行网络配置时,可以通过此接口获取相关信息。使用该接口的前提条件是用户已登录并具有查询实例Tor信息的权限,且指定的实例已存在。查询操作完成后,接口将返回指定实例的Tor信息。若用户无权限操作、指定的实例不存在或实例未连接到Tor交换机,接口将返回相应的错误信息。","operationId":"GetTopologies","parameters":[{"$ref":"#/parameters/projectId"},{"description":"**参数解释**:Lite Server实例ID。\n**约束限制**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","in":"query","name":"id","required":false,"type":"string"},{"description":"**参数解释**:Lite Server实例对应的资源ID。\n**约束限制**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","in":"query","name":"resource_id","required":false,"type":"string"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"**参数解释**:查询实例的Tor信息响应体。","examples":{"application/json":{"servers":[{"network_nodes":["11.172.213.11","11.172.213.12"],"resource_id":"3efd3a22